channel.title: MY server is 95% up but i cant or my friends cant go on it!
channel.description:
So i've made this server, From scratch! So i run it, And i try to go on, It sais its not on, I then go to google.com status checker and it sais that my ip wich i got from www.whatsmyip.org is online! I turn on my desktop and logon to it, but it still sais im offline! I then go back to google and try my no-ip ( yes no-ip duc is downloaded! ) It sais it is offline, I've portforwarded, but i think i dont need to ebcause i have that dsl/verizon router/box! I need someones help ASAP!
Edit: 2 PEOPLE HAVE JUST GONE ON, BUT ME AND MY FRIEND NEXT TO ME ON YM DESKTOP STILL CANT GET ON
[img]http://www.google.com/tools/statusimg.php?ip=151.198.119.121&port=43594[/img]
^ its online -.-
EDIT NUMBER 2!: when i go to portforward it asks for Global port start, Global port end, and base hostport
WHAT DO I PUT IN FOR THESE 3?
